Tune in live and watch the action unfold as BMSD 2025 pushes the competition Beyond Limits!

FS eSports

myG Los Hermanos

4TR Official
NoNx Esports
Gods Omen

iQOO ORANGUTAN

Group C
Victores Sumus

MEDAL ESPORTS

Match 6: Erangel–GROUP–A vs C

snippet.title: Dholida Dhol Re Vagade DJ Remix | Trending Gujarati Garba Song of Navratri 2025 | Dandiya Night Hits
snippet.description:
🎶 Dholida, dhol re vagade… Garba Ramva no samay aavyo re – DJ Remix Gujarati Garba Song | Trending Song of Navratri 2025 | Dandiya Night Hits 💃🕺

Welcome to Ishtar Gujarati, your ultimate destination for the best Gujarati songs, Garba hits, Navratri special tracks, and devotional music. This Navratri 2025, we bring you the all-time favorite and most energetic Gujarati Garba song – “Dholida Dhol Re Vagade”. Known for its powerful beats, traditional vibes, and festive spirit, this song has become a must-play at every Garba ground, Dandiya night, and Navratri celebration.

#DholidaDholReVagade #GujaratiGarba #IshtarGujarati #Navratri2025 #GarbaSongs #DandiyaNight #GujaratiSong #NavratriSpecial #GarbaDance #TrendingGarba #djremix 

✨ About the Song
Dholida Dhol Re Vagade is one of the most loved Gujarati Garba tracks that captures the true essence of Navratri celebrations. With its rhythmic dhol beats and soulful Gujarati lyrics, it creates the perfect atmosphere for Garba lovers across the globe. Whether you are in Ahmedabad, Surat, Vadodara, Rajkot, or celebrating Navratri internationally in the USA, UK, Canada, or Australia – this song unites Gujaratis everywhere in devotion and dance.

✨ Why This Song is Perfect for Navratri 2025

Energetic Garba beats that make everyone dance.

A trending Navratri song that’s loved by both youth and elders.

Ideal for Dandiya competitions, Garba nights, and cultural events.

Brings alive the spirit of Maa Durga’s blessings through music and rhythm.

One of the most requested Gujarati Garba songs on dance floors during Navratri.

✨ Celebrate Navratri with Ishtar Gujarati
At Ishtar Gujarati, we aim to bring you not just songs, but memories and traditions through music. Our channel is home to:

Traditional Gujarati Garba songs 🎵

Latest Navratri 2025 Dandiya hits 💃

Folk songs from Gujarat 🌸

Devotional bhajans and Mataji songs 🙏

Festival special music playlists 🌟

✨ Dholida Dhol Re Vagade – A Song of Tradition & Energy
Garba is not just a dance, it is an emotion for Gujaratis. From kids to elders, everyone circles around the garba ground to celebrate the victory of good over evil during Navratri. The beats of Dholida Dhol Re Vagade fill every heart with joy, reminding us of our roots and culture. The track is timeless and continues to be a favorite Garba anthem year after year.

✨ Global Gujarati Celebration
This song is not limited to Gujarat alone. During Navratri 2025, Gujarati communities worldwide celebrate with Garba and Dandiya events. From New Jersey to London, Toronto to Sydney, Dholida Dhol Re Vagade will echo in Garba halls, temples, and cultural gatherings.

✨ How to Enjoy This Song

Play it loud during your Navratri Garba nights.

Add it to your Dandiya playlist for festive vibes.

Share it with friends and family to spread the joy.

Use it as background music for your Navratri reels and shorts.

✨ Ishtar Gujarati – Your Navratri Music Partner
We at Ishtar Gujarati are committed to delivering high-quality music for every Gujarati household. Our mission is to keep traditions alive by offering you timeless folk, trending Garba songs, and devotional tracks that connect with your heart and soul.

🙏 Blessings of Maa Durga
This Navratri, let the blessings of Maa Durga bring prosperity, happiness, and positivity in your life. Dance your heart out to Dholida Dhol Re Vagade and keep the festive spirit alive.

Welcome to Ishtar Gujarati, your ultimate destination for the best Gujarati songs, Garba hits, Navratri special tracks, and devotional music. This Navratri 2025, we bring you the all-time favorite and most energetic Gujarati Garba song – “Dholida Dhol Re Vagade”. Known for its powerful beats, traditional vibes, and festive spirit, this song has become a must-play at every Garba ground, Dandiya night, and Navratri celebration.

#DholidaDholReVagade #GujaratiGarba #IshtarGujarati #Navratri2025 #GarbaSongs #DandiyaNight #GujaratiSong #NavratriSpecial #GarbaDance #TrendingGarba #djremix 

✨ About the Song
Dholida Dhol Re Vagade is one of the most loved Gujarati Garba tracks that captures the true essence of Navratri celebrations. With its rhythmic dhol beats and soulful Gujarati lyrics, it creates the perfect atmosphere for Garba lovers across the globe. Whether you are in Ahmedabad, Surat, Vadodara, Rajkot, or celebrating Navratri internationally in the USA, UK, Canada, or Australia – this song unites Gujaratis everywhere in devotion and dance.

Energetic Garba beats that make everyone dance.

A trending Navratri song that’s loved by both youth and elders.

✨ Dholida Dhol Re Vagade – A Song of Tradition & Energy
Garba is not just a dance, it is an emotion for Gujaratis. From kids to elders, everyone circles around the garba ground to celebrate the victory of good over evil during Navratri. The beats of Dholida Dhol Re Vagade fill every heart with joy, reminding us of our roots and culture. The track is timeless and continues to be a favorite Garba anthem year after year.

✨ Global Gujarati Celebration
This song is not limited to Gujarat alone. During Navratri 2025, Gujarati communities worldwide celebrate with Garba and Dandiya events. From New Jersey to London, Toronto to Sydney, Dholida Dhol Re Vagade will echo in Garba halls, temples, and cultural gatherings.

✨ How to Enjoy This Song

Play it loud during your Navratri Garba nights.

Add it to your Dandiya playlist for festive vibes.

Share it with friends and family to spread the joy.

Use it as background music for your Navratri reels and shorts.

✨ Ishtar Gujarati – Your Navratri Music Partner
We at Ishtar Gujarati are committed to delivering high-quality music for every Gujarati household. Our mission is to keep traditions alive by offering you timeless folk, trending Garba songs, and devotional tracks that connect with your heart and soul.

snippet.title: Avatar: Fire and Ash | New Trailer
snippet.description:
This world is much deeper than you imagine. Watch the brand-new trailer for Avatar: Fire and Ash and experience it in theatres December 19th.

Also, don’t miss Avatar: The Way of Water back on the big screen in 3D for one week only, starting October 3rd.

With “Avatar: Fire and Ash,” James Cameron takes audiences back to Pandora in an immersive new adventure with Marine turned Na’vi leader Jake Sully (Sam Worthington), Na’vi warrior Neytiri (Zoe Saldaña), and the Sully family. The film, which has a screenplay by James Cameron & Rick Jaffa & Amanda Silver, and a story by James Cameron & Rick Jaffa & Amanda Silver & Josh Friedman & Shane Salerno, also stars Sigourney Weaver, Stephen Lang, Oona Chaplin, Cliff Curtis, Joel David Moore, CCH Pounder, Edie Falco, David Thewlis, Jemaine Clement, Giovanni Ribisi, Britain Dalton, Jamie Flatters, Trinity Jo-Li Bliss, Jack Champion, Brendan Cowell, Bailey Bass, Filip Geljo, Duane Evans, Jr., and Kate Winslet.

This world is much deeper than you imagine. Watch the brand-new trailer for Avatar: Fire and Ash and experience it in theatres December 19th.

Also, don’t miss Avatar: The Way of Water back on the big screen in 3D for one week only, starting October 3rd.

With “Avatar: Fire and Ash,” James Cameron takes audiences back to Pandora in an immersive new adventure with Marine turned Na’vi leader Jake Sully (Sam Worthington), Na’vi warrior Neytiri (Zoe Saldaña), and the Sully family. The film, which has a screenplay by James Cameron & Rick Jaffa & Amanda Silver, and a story by James Cameron & Rick Jaffa & Amanda Silver & Josh Friedman & Shane Salerno, also stars Sigourney Weaver, Stephen Lang, Oona Chaplin, Cliff Curtis, Joel David Moore, CCH Pounder, Edie Falco, David Thewlis, Jemaine Clement, Giovanni Ribisi, Britain Dalton, Jamie Flatters, Trinity Jo-Li Bliss, Jack Champion, Brendan Cowell, Bailey Bass, Filip Geljo, Duane Evans, Jr., and Kate Winslet.

——
ABOUT AVATAR
Director: James Cameron
Cast: Sam Worthington, Zoe Saldaña, Sigourney Weaver, Stephen Lang
Films: Avatar & Avatar: The Way of Water

हा आवे तो आजा झूठी बात क्यों बनावे,,
दो महीना से रानी येठ क्यों दिखावे

गोली नींद की दे अइयो सो जावे संजना,,

Ha baat banave bethi bethi angana,,
Goli need ki de aiyo so jaave sajna

Ha karle savar babu milne bhi aaungi ,,
Pyar ki hai pyas pani hath se pilaungi,,,
Pyar se bdo koi rog hath na,
Payal ki khanak se jagenge sajna,,

Chhati se lagake deja moku sakun so,,

khoon  so jalave gori tera hasna,,

snippet.title: Marvel’s Wolverine - Gameplay Trailer | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
Become a living weapon. As he searches for answers about his past, Wolverine will do whatever it takes – unleashing brutal claw combat, violent rage, and relentless determination – to cut through the mystery of the man he used to be. 
 
 From Insomniac Games, the developers of the critically acclaimed Marvel’s Spider-Man franchise, comes Marvel’s Wolverine, an all-new take on an iconic character based on Marvel Comics. Developed in collaboration with Marvel Games and Sony Interactive Entertainment, Marvel’s Wolverine coming to PlayStation®5 consoles Fall 2026.

snippet.title: HAQ | Official Teaser | Yami Gautam Dhar, Emraan Hashmi | Suparn S Varma | In Cinemas 7th Nov
snippet.description:
Shazia Bano takes her husband Abbas to court after he abandons her and their children, sparking a national battle over faith, women’s rights, and justice. Inspired by the landmark Supreme Court judgement of Mohd. Ahmed Khan vs. Shah Bano Begum. Haq is the story of one woman’s fight for her rights and justice. 

Releasing in cinemas on 7th November

HAQ is a fictionalized and dramatized version of events stated in the book titled ‘Bano: Bharat ki Beti’ written by Jigna Vora.

Cast- Yami Gautam, Emraan Hashmi, Vartika Singh, Danish Husain, Sheeba Chadha,
Aseem Hattangady
Directed by- Suparn S Varma
Written by- Reshu Nath
Produced by- Vineet Jain
Produced by- Vishal Gurnani, Juhi Parekh Mehta, Harman Baweja
Co- Producer- Amrita Pandey
Co-Producer- Suparn S Varma, Rowena Baweja, Sandeep Singh
Supervising Producer (Insomnia Films)- Vicky Jain

Director of Photography- Pratham Mehta
Associate Producer- Kalpesh Damani
Supervising Producer- Shraddha Chauhan
Executive Producers- Ramesh G Yadav, Priyanka Mehrotra
Production Designers- Abhijit Gaonkar, Sonam Singh

VP, Marketing- Ishwinder Arora

चौथे नवरात्रे को, भक्त तुझे ध्याते,

localized.description:
#navratrispecial2025 #shardiyanavratri #maakushmanda #trending 

शारदीय नवरात्रि स्पेशल - Maa Kushmanda Ki Aarti  जय कुष्मांडा माता - माँ कुष्मांडा की आरती.

@BhaktiBhajanSagar0 

Album : Jai Kushmanda Mata
Singer :  Ruchi Khandelwal
Producer : Bhakti Bhajan Sagar
Music : Shankar Maheshwari
Lyrics : Traditional
Channel : Bhakti Bhajan Sagar

#shardiyanavratrispecial2025
#maakushmandaaarti
#jaikushmandamata
#शारदीयनवरात्रिस्पेशल
#माँकुष्मांडाकीआरती
#Maakushmandaaarti
#जयकुष्मांडामाता
#माँकुष्मांडाकीआरती
#navratri2025
#Jaikhusmandamata 
#deviaarti 
#navratriaarti

माँ आरती तेरी गाते, मैया आरती तेरी गाते,
कुष्मांडा महामाया, हम तुमको ध्याते,
माँ आरती तेरी गाते

हे जगदम्ब द्यामयी, आदि स्वरूपा माँ,
देव ऋषि मुनि ज्ञानी, गुण तेरे गाते,
माँ आरती तेरी गाते

कर ब्रह्माण्ड की रचना, कुष्मांडा कहलाये,
वेद पुराण भवानी, सब यही बतलाते,
माँ आरती तेरी गाते

सूर्य लोक निवासिनी, तुमको कोटी प्रणाम,
सम्मुख तेरे पाप और, दोष ना टिक पाते,
माँ आरती तेरी गाते

अष्ट भुजे महाशक्ति, सिंह वाहिनी है तू,
भव सिंधु से तरते, दर्शन जो पाते,
माँ आरती तेरी गाते

अष्ट सिद्धि नौ निधियाँ, हाथ तेरे माता,
पा जाते है सहज ही, जो तुमको ध्याते,
माँ आरती तेरी गाते

शास्त्र विधि से विधिवत, जो पूजन करते,
आदि शक्ति जगजननी, तेरी द्या पाते,
माँ आरती तेरी गाते

नवदुर्गो में मैया, चौथा स्थान तेरा,
चौथे नवरात्रे को, भक्त तुझे ध्याते,
माँ आरती तेरी गाते

आधि व्याधि सब हरके, सुख समृद्धि दो,
हे जगदम्ब भवानी, इतनी द्या चाहते,
माँ आरती तेरी गाते

कुष्मांडा जी की आरती, जो कोई गावे,
कहत शिवानंद स्वामी, मनवांछित फल पावे,
माँ आरती तेरी गाते

Sung and written by Badshah & Simiran Kaur Dhadli, with beats by Hiten, this track is bold, raw, and unforgettable.

Tu hai bandi ghalat

mohol badalati hai kaise

Buri aafat tu
Buri aadat tu

Kokaina ina ina ina ina ina ina (mujhe hit karti hai jaise)

Yeh pareshan karegi 
Leke jaan rahegi
Bada nuksaan karegi
Aaj koi kaand karegi

Tu hi hai alpha tu hi hai beta
Galt jo dekhe tujhe
Tujhe tod du gita 
saanvle rang ki nagin jaisi
Hit karti hai jaise chitta

Aaju baaju na koi fatakra 
Launda koi na palk jhapakra
Tar tar tar hai Paseena tapakra
Vo bhi ni hatri mai bhi ni hatra

Kamar ghuma
aane de paseena

game me apna bhi tod koi na

snippet.description:

#payalkikhanak 
#पायल_की_खनक
#payal_ki_khanak

anil rawat viral song

payal ki khanak viral song



हो कैसे आऊ मिलवे बजेंगे कंगना 
पायल की खनक से जगेंगे सजना,,

हा आवे तो आजा झूठी बात क्यों बनावे,,
दो महीना से रानी येठ क्यों दिखावे 

हा बात बनावे बैठी बैठी अंगना,,
गोली नींद की दे अइयो सो जावे संजना,,

हा करले सवर बाबू मिलने भी आऊंगी,,
प्यार की है प्यास पानी हाथ से पिलाऊंगी,,

प्यार से बडो कोई रोग हतना,,
पायल की खनक से जगेंगे सजना,,

न चहिए प्यार मोकू बारिश की बूंद को,,
छाती से लगाके देजा मौकु सकून सो,,

हा खून सो जलावे गोरी तेरा हंसना,,
गोली नींद की दे अइयो सो जाएंगे सजना,,

Ho kese aau milve bajenge kangna,,
Payal ki khanak se jagenge sajna 

Aave to aaja jhuti baat Kyo banave,,
Do mahina se rani yeth kyo dikhave,,
Ha baat banave bethi bethi angana,,
Goli need ki de aiyo so jaave sajna

Ha karle savar babu milne bhi aaungi ,,
Pyar ki hai pyas pani hath se pilaungi,,,
Pyar se bdo koi rog hath na,
Payal ki khanak se jagenge sajna,,

N chahiye pyar moku barish ki bund ko,,
Chhati se lagake deja moku sakun so,,

khoon  so jalave gori tera hasna,,
Goli need ki de aiyo so jaave sajna,,,

पायल की खनक से जगेंगे सजना,,

हा आवे तो आजा झूठी बात क्यों बनावे,,
दो महीना से रानी येठ क्यों दिखावे 

हा बात बनावे बैठी बैठी अंगना,,
गोली नींद की दे अइयो सो जावे संजना,,

छाती से लगाके देजा मौकु सकून सो,,

हा खून सो जलावे गोरी तेरा हंसना,,
गोली नींद की दे अइयो सो जाएंगे सजना,,

Ho kese aau milve bajenge kangna,,
Payal ki khanak se jagenge sajna 

Aave to aaja jhuti baat Kyo banave,,
Do mahina se rani yeth kyo dikhave,,
Ha baat banave bethi bethi angana,,
Goli need ki de aiyo so jaave sajna

Ha karle savar babu milne bhi aaungi ,,
Pyar ki hai pyas pani hath se pilaungi,,,
Pyar se bdo koi rog hath na,
Payal ki khanak se jagenge sajna,,

N chahiye pyar moku barish ki bund ko,,
Chhati se lagake deja moku sakun so,,

khoon  so jalave gori tera hasna,,
Goli need ki de aiyo so jaave sajna,,,

snippet.title: প্ৰতিদিনে | Protidine | Zubeen Garg | Rodor Sithi | Heart Touching Assamese Song | New Sad Song
snippet.description:
Times Music Axom proudly presents the audio version of “Protidine”, a deeply moving song by the legendary Zubeen Garg from the acclaimed Assamese movie “Rodor Sithi.” Known for his ability to convey raw emotion through his music, Zubeen Garg’s soulful voice in Protidine touches the heart, capturing the essence of love, longing, and everyday emotions. The song’s simple yet powerful melody, paired with meaningful lyrics, makes it a timeless favorite among Assamese music lovers and a beautiful representation of contemporary Assamese cinema.

Whether you’re a fan of Zubeen Garg’s iconic voice or someone exploring Assamese music for the first time, Protidine is a perfect listen that resonates with universal feelings and cultural depth. This audio release by Times Music Axom ensures that the magic of Rodor Sithi’s soundtrack reaches every home, keeping the spirit of Assamese music alive and thriving.

snippet.title: Navratri 2025 Special |Jagdamba Ghar Main Diyara Baar Aini | Kalpana Patowary | Paramparik Devi Geet
snippet.description:
✨ Presenting the soulful Bhojpuri Devi Geet “Jagdamba Ghar Main Diyara Baar Aani” sung by the melodious Kalpana Patowary.
This bhajan is dedicated to Maa Jagdamba, celebrating the divine light, faith, and devotion during festive nights.

Make Reels on Instagram:-
♪ Instagram -  

CP - 
♪ Song: Jagdamba Ghar Main Diyara Baar Aini
♪ Singer: Kalpana Patowary
♪ Lyrics: Amit G Tiwari ( Katha Vachak ) 
♪ Music: Kanha Singh
♪ Video by: Aman Gupta
♪ Music Lable: CIC PICTURES
♪ Produced by: Nitish Singh
♪ Project Head : Virat Sharma 
---------------------------------------------------------
 Full Song Available On ♪ 
♪ Spotify: 
♪ Jiosaavn: 
♪ Wynk: 
♪ Apple Music: 
♪ YT Music:   
♪ Amazon Music: 
♪ Gaana:

Lyrics: -
बार अइनी बार अइनी बार अइनी हो
जगदम्बा घर में दियरा बार अइनी हो.....
जय भगवति देवि नमो वरदे, जय पापविनाशिनि बहुफलदे।
जय शुम्भनिशुम्भकपालधरे, प्रणमामि तु देवि नरार्तिहरे

गांव के पुरुब काली मइया के मंदिरवा हो 
भोरे भोरे मंदिर बहार अइनी हो
जगदम्बा घर में दियरा बार अइनी हो

लाले लाले चुनरी से मइया के सिंगार कइनी..
भरी भरी अंखियों निहार अइनी हो 
जगदम्बा घर में दियरा बार अइनी हो

श्रद्धा के दीपक,प्रेम के बाती हो 
मइया के आरती उतार अइनी हो
जगदम्बा घर में दियरा बार अइनी हो

नवरात्रि का चौथा दिन~ माँ कुष्मांडा की आरती | ॐ जय कुष्मांडा माता Kushmanda Aarti,Navratri Day-4 

नवरात्र-पूजन के चौथे दिन कूष्माण्डा देवी के स्वरूप की उपासना की जाती है। इस दिन साधक का मन 'अनाहत' चक्र में अवस्थित होता है। अतः इस दिन उसे अत्यंत पवित्र और अचंचल मन से कूष्माण्डा देवी के स्वरूप को ध्यान में रखकर पूजा-उपासना के कार्य में लगना चाहिए।

हरा हरा Heart shape ka patta,
Hara hara heart shape ka patta! 🍀

Desi vibes, full-on energy! 🔥 Watch the lyrical video of ‘Panwadi’ from ‘Sunny Sanskari Ki Tulsi Kumari’, featuring Varun Dhawan, Janhvi Kapoor, Rohit Saraf & Sanya Malhotra. Sung by Khesari Lal Yadav, Masoom Sharma, Dev Negi, Pritam, Nikhita Gandhi & AKASA – this track is pure party madness! 🍃🎶

#Panwadi #KhesariLalYadav #MasoomSharma #VarunDhawan #JanhviKapoor #RohitSaraf #SanyaMalhotra #DevNegi #Pritam #NikhitaGandhi #AKASA

Music - A.P.S
Lyrics -  Jairaj

Bhojpuri Traditional Folk Performed by Khesari Lal Yadav
Haryanvi Traditional Folk Performed by Masoom Sharma
Rap Performed by Siva G

Sound Design - Ashwin Kulkarni, DJ Phukan

Studio Assistants - Ameya Dayal, Khush Jaggi, Jaibir Singh

Musicians:

Accordion- Salamon Eredics

snippet.description:
PMC Marathi Presents 
-------------
Aigiri Nandini With Lyrics | Mahishasura Mardini | Anjali Goyal | महिषासुर मर्दिनी स्तोत्र | Stotra

Credits:
Title : Aigiri Nandini
Singer: Anjali Goyal
Music Director: Gandhi Brothers (Prakash-Subhash Gandhi)
Language: Sanskrit
Label: PMC Marathi Bhakti
Copyrights :- PMCC Multimedia Pvt Ltd

Lyrics:
॥ महिषासुर मर्दिनि स्तोत्रम् ॥
अयि गिरिनन्दिनि नन्दितमेदिनि विश्वविनोदिनि नन्दिनुते

गिरिवरविन्ध्यशिरोऽधिनिवासिनि विष्णुविलासिनि जिष्णुनुते।

भगवति हे शितिकण्ठकुटुम्बिनि भूरिकुटुम्बिनि भूरिकृते

जय जय हे महिषासुरमर्दिनि रम्यकपर्दिनि शैलसुते॥1॥

सुरवरवर्षिणि दुर्धरधर्षिणि दुर्मुखमर्षिणि हर्षरते

त्रिभुवनपोषिणि शङ्करतोषिणि किल्बिषमोषिणि घोषरते

दनुजनिरोषिणि दितिसुतरोषिणि दुर्मदशोषिणि सिन्धुसुते

जय जय हे महिषासुरमर्दिनि रम्यकपर्दिनि शैलसुते॥2॥

अयि जगदम्ब मदम्ब कदम्ब वनप्रियवासिनि हासरते

शिखरि शिरोमणि तुङ्गहिमलय शृङ्गनिजालय मध्यगते।

मधुमधुरे मधुकैटभगञ्जिनि कैटभभञ्जिनि रासरते

जय जय हे महिषासुरमर्दिनि रम्यकपर्दिनि शैलसुते॥3॥

अयि शतखण्ड विखण्डितरुण्ड वितुण्डितशुण्द गजाधिपते

रिपुगजगण्ड विदारणचण्ड पराक्रमशुण्ड मृगाधिपते।

निजभुजदण्ड निपातितखण्ड विपातितमुण्ड भटाधिपते

जय जय हे महिषासुरमर्दिनि रम्यकपर्दिनि शैलसुते॥4॥

अयि रणदुर्मद शत्रुवधोदित दुर्धरनिर्जर शक्तिभृते

चतुरविचार धुरीणमहाशिव दूतकृत प्रमथाधिपते।

दुरितदुरीह दुराशयदुर्मति दानवदुत कृतान्तमते

जय जय हे महिषासुरमर्दिनि रम्यकपर्दिनि शैलसुते॥5॥

अयि शरणागत वैरिवधुवर वीरवराभय दायकरे

त्रिभुवनमस्तक शुलविरोधि शिरोऽधिकृतामल शुलकरे।

दुमिदुमितामर धुन्दुभिनादमहोमुखरीकृत दिङ्मकरे

जय जय हे महिषासुरमर्दिनि रम्यकपर्दिनि शैलसुते॥6॥

अयि निजहुङ्कृति मात्रनिराकृत धूम्रविलोचन धूम्रशते

समरविशोषित शोणितबीज समुद्भवशोणित बीजलते।

शिवशिवशुम्भ निशुम्भमहाहव तर्पितभूत पिशाचरते

जय जय हे महिषासुरमर्दिनि रम्यकपर्दिनि शैलसुते॥7॥

धनुरनुषङ्ग रणक्षणसङ्ग परिस्फुरदङ्ग नटत्कटके

कनकपिशङ्ग पृषत्कनिषङ्ग रसद्भटशृङ्ग हताबटुके।

कृतचतुरङ्ग बलक्षितिरङ्ग घटद्बहुरङ्ग रटद्बटुके

जय जय हे महिषासुरमर्दिनि रम्यकपर्दिनि शैलसुते॥8॥

सुरललना ततथेयि तथेयि कृताभिनयोदर नृत्यरते

कृत कुकुथः कुकुथो गडदादिकताल कुतूहल गानरते।

धुधुकुट धुक्कुट धिंधिमित ध्वनि धीर मृदंग निनादरते

जय जय हे महिषासुरमर्दिनि रम्यकपर्दिनि शैलसुते॥9॥

जय जय जप्य जयेजयशब्द परस्तुति तत्परविश्वनुते

झणझणझिञ्झिमि झिङ्कृत नूपुरशिञ्जितमोहित भूतपते।

नटित नटार्ध नटी नट नायक नाटितनाट्य सुगानरते

जय जय हे महिषासुरमर्दिनि रम्यकपर्दिनि शैलसुते॥10॥

अयि सुमनःसुमनःसुमनः सुमनःसुमनोहरकान्तियुते

श्रितरजनी रजनीरजनी रजनीरजनी करवक्त्रवृते।

सुनयनविभ्रमर भ्रमरभ्रमर भ्रमरभ्रमराधिपते

जय जय हे महिषासुरमर्दिनि रम्यकपर्दिनि शैलसुते॥11॥

सहितमहाहव मल्लमतल्लिक मल्लितरल्लक मल्लरते

विरचितवल्लिक पल्लिकमल्लिक झिल्लिकभिल्लिक वर्गवृते।

शितकृतफुल्ल समुल्लसितारुण तल्लजपल्लव सल्ललिते

जय जय हे महिषासुरमर्दिनि रम्यकपर्दिनि शैलसुते॥12॥

अविरलगण्ड गलन्मदमेदुर मत्तमतङ्ग जराजपते

त्रिभुवनभुषण भूतकलानिधि रूपपयोनिधि राजसुते।

अयि सुदतीजन लालसमानस मोहन मन्मथराजसुते

जय जय हे महिषासुरमर्दिनि रम्यकपर्दिनि शैलसुते॥13॥

कमलदलामल कोमलकान्ति कलाकलितामल भाललते

सकलविलास कलानिलयक्रम केलिचलत्कल हंसकुले।

अलिकुलसङ्कुल कुवलयमण्डल मौलिमिलद्बकुलालिकुले

जय जय हे महिषासुरमर्दिनि रम्यकपर्दिनि शैलसुते॥14॥

करमुरलीरव वीजितकूजित लज्जितकोकिल मञ्जुमते

मिलितपुलिन्द मनोहरगुञ्जित रञ्जितशैल निकुञ्जगते।

निजगणभूत महाशबरीगण सद्गुणसम्भृत केलितले

जय जय हे महिषासुरमर्दिनि रम्यकपर्दिनि शैलसुते॥15॥

कटितटपीत दुकूलविचित्र मयुखतिरस्कृत चन्द्ररुचे

प्रणतसुरासुर मौलिमणिस्फुर दंशुलसन्नख चन्द्ररुचे

जितकनकाचल मौलिमदोर्जित निर्भरकुञ्जर कुम्भकुचे

जय जय हे महिषासुरमर्दिनि रम्यकपर्दिनि शैलसुते॥16॥

विजितसहस्रकरैक सहस्रकरैक सहस्रकरैकनुते

कृतसुरतारक सङ्गरतारक सङ्गरतारक सूनुसुते।

सुरथसमाधि समानसमाधि समाधिसमाधि सुजातरते।

जय जय हे महिषासुरमर्दिनि रम्यकपर्दिनि शैलसुते॥17॥

पदकमलं करुणानिलये वरिवस्यति योऽनुदिनं सुशिवे

अयि कमले कमलानिलये कमलानिलयः स कथं न भवेत्।

तव पदमेव परम्पदमित्यनुशीलयतो मम किं न शिवे

जय जय हे महिषासुरमर्दिनि रम्यकपर्दिनि शैलसुते॥18॥

कनकलसत्कलसिन्धुजलैरनुषिञ्चति तेगुणरङ्गभुवम्

भजति स किं न शचीकुचकुम्भतटीपरिरम्भसुखानुभवम्।

तव चरणं शरणं करवाणि नतामरवाणि निवासि शिवम्

जय जय हे महिषासुरमर्दिनि रम्यकपर्दिनि शैलसुते॥19॥

तव विमलेन्दुकुलं वदनेन्दुमलं सकलं ननु कूलयते

किमु पुरुहूतपुरीन्दु मुखी सुमुखीभिरसौ विमुखीक्रियते।

मम तु मतं शिवनामधने भवती कृपया किमुत क्रियते

जय जय हे महिषासुरमर्दिनि रम्यकपर्दिनि शैलसुते॥20॥

अयि मयि दीन दयालुतया कृपयैव त्वया भवितव्यमुमे

अयि जगतो जननी कृपयासि यथासि तथानुमितासिरते।

यदुचितमत्र भवत्युररीकुरुतादुरुतापमपाकुरुते

जय जय हे महिषासुरमर्दिनि रम्यकपर्दिनि शैलसुते॥21॥

---------------

#PMCC7560

॥ महिषासुर मर्दिनि स्तोत्रम् ॥

जय जय हे महिषासुरमर्दिनि रम्यकपर्दिनि शैलसुते॥3॥

अयि शतखण्ड विखण्डितरुण्ड वितुण्डितशुण्द गजाधिपते

रिपुगजगण्ड विदारणचण्ड पराक्रमशुण्ड मृगाधिपते।

निजभुजदण्ड निपातितखण्ड विपातितमुण्ड भटाधिपते

जय जय हे महिषासुरमर्दिनि रम्यकपर्दिनि शैलसुते॥4॥

अयि रणदुर्मद शत्रुवधोदित दुर्धरनिर्जर शक्तिभृते

चतुरविचार धुरीणमहाशिव दूतकृत प्रमथाधिपते।

दुरितदुरीह दुराशयदुर्मति दानवदुत कृतान्तमते

जय जय हे महिषासुरमर्दिनि रम्यकपर्दिनि शैलसुते॥5॥

सकलविलास कलानिलयक्रम केलिचलत्कल हंसकुले।

करमुरलीरव वीजितकूजित लज्जितकोकिल मञ्जुमते

मिलितपुलिन्द मनोहरगुञ्जित रञ्जितशैल निकुञ्जगते।

#Ambey_Tu_hai_Jagdambey_Kali #Om_Jai_Ambey_Gauri_Arti
#bhor_bhai_din_chad_gaya_meri_ambey 
#omjaiambegauri 



भोर भई दिन चढ़ गया मेरी अम्बे,
हो रही जय जय कार मंदिर विच आरती जय माँ ।
हे दरबारा वाली आरती जय माँ ।
ओ पहाड़ा वाली आरती जय माँ ॥

काहे दी मैया तेरी आरती बनावा,
काहे दी पावां विच बाती,
मंदिर विच आरती जय माँ ।
सुहे चोलेयाँ वाली आरती जय माँ ।
हे माँ पहाड़ा वाली आरती जय माँ ॥

अम्बे तू है जगदम्बे काली,
जय दुर्गे खप्पर वाली,
तेर ही गुण गायें भारती,
ओ मैया हम सब उतारे तेरी आरती ।

तेर भक्त जानो पर मैया भीड़ पड़ी है भारी,
दानव दल पर टूट पड़ो माँ कर के सिंह सवारी ।
सो सो सिंघो से है बलशाली,
है दस भुजाओं वाली,
दुखिओं के दुखड़े निवारती ।

जय अम्बे गौरी,
मैया जय श्यामा गौरी ।
तुमको निशदिन ध्यावत,
हरि ब्रह्मा शिवरी ॥
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी..॥

मांग सिंदूर विराजत,
टीको मृगमद को ।
उज्ज्वल से दोउ नैना,
चंद्रवदन नीको ॥
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी..॥

तेर भक्त जानो पर मैया भीड़ पड़ी है भारी,
दानव दल पर टूट पड़ो माँ कर के सिंह सवारी ।
सो सो सिंघो से है बलशाली,
है दस भुजाओं वाली,
दुखिओं के दुखड़े निवारती ।

जय अम्बे गौरी,
मैया जय श्यामा गौरी ।
तुमको निशदिन ध्यावत,
हरि ब्रह्मा शिवरी ॥
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी..॥

मांग सिंदूर विराजत,
टीको मृगमद को ।
उज्ज्वल से दोउ नैना,
चंद्रवदन नीको ॥
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी..॥

snippet.title: नवरात्रि के पांचवें दिन मां स्कंद माता की कथा | Navratri Day 5 - Maa skandmata ki katha
snippet.description:
नवरात्रि के पांचवें दिन मां स्कंद माता की कथा | Navratri Day 5 - Maa skandmata ki katha 

Best wishes to everyone on the fifth day of Navratri. Skandamata is worshiped on the fifth day of Navratri. Maa #Skandamata​ is the fifth incarnation of Goddess Durga. The word Skandmata is made up of two words - Skanda and Mata. Skanda is another name for Lord Kartikeya, Kartikeya is the son of Bholenath and Parvati mother and brother of Ganesha. Mata means mother and thus Skandamata means mother of Kartikeya. Hence Skandamata is a form of Maa Parvati.
Goddess Durga has four arms in the form of Skandamata. She is holding Kartikeya (Skanda) in one hand, holds a lotus in the other and third hand and blesses the devotees with the fourth hand. She rides a lion and sits on a lotus, which is why she is also called Padmasana. Karthikeya is known as Murugan in South India. He is the commander-in-chief of the army of gods.  Worshiping Maa Skandamata awakens the Vishuddhi Chakra, through which effect one attains the attainment of speech, increases in age and becomes a scholar. The worship of Skandmata leads to the knowledge of sixteen arts and sixteen figures. There is an interesting story of the birth of Karthikeya.Let us now hear the story of Mother Skanda Mata and know that the puja vidhi of Mother Skanda Mata. The story of Skanda Mata reveals who the Goddess Skanda Mata is. How did the goddess get this name of Skanda Mata? In this video Skanda Mata Aarti, Skanda Mata Mantra, Skanda Mata Kavach and Skanda Mata Stotram are also shown

hi.title: नवरात्रि के पांचवें दिन मां स्कंद माता की कथा | Navratri Day 5 - Maa skandmata ki katha
hi.description:
नवरात्रि के पांचवें दिन मां स्कंद माता की कथा | Navratri Day 5 - Maa skandmata ki katha 

Best wishes to everyone on the fifth day of Navratri. Skandamata is worshiped on the fifth day of Navratri. Maa #Skandamata​ is the fifth incarnation of Goddess Durga. The word Skandmata is made up of two words - Skanda and Mata. Skanda is another name for Lord Kartikeya, Kartikeya is the son of Bholenath and Parvati mother and brother of Ganesha. Mata means mother and thus Skandamata means mother of Kartikeya. Hence Skandamata is a form of Maa Parvati.
Goddess Durga has four arms in the form of Skandamata. She is holding Kartikeya (Skanda) in one hand, holds a lotus in the other and third hand and blesses the devotees with the fourth hand. She rides a lion and sits on a lotus, which is why she is also called Padmasana. Karthikeya is known as Murugan in South India. He is the commander-in-chief of the army of gods.  Worshiping Maa Skandamata awakens the Vishuddhi Chakra, through which effect one attains the attainment of speech, increases in age and becomes a scholar. The worship of Skandmata leads to the knowledge of sixteen arts and sixteen figures. There is an interesting story of the birth of Karthikeya.Let us now hear the story of Mother Skanda Mata and know that the puja vidhi of Mother Skanda Mata. The story of Skanda Mata reveals who the Goddess Skanda Mata is. How did the goddess get this name of Skanda Mata? In this video Skanda Mata Aarti, Skanda Mata Mantra, Skanda Mata Kavach and Skanda Mata Stotram are also shown

snippet.title: 🌸 Sri Annapoornadevi Chalisa | Navaratri Special | Divine Devotional Song | Sri Annapurna Devi Songs
snippet.description:
🙏🌺 Sri Annapoornadevi Chalisa 🌺🙏
Experience the divine grace of Goddess Annapoornadevi, the giver of food, nourishment, and abundance, through this sacred Chalisa. On this auspicious occasion of Navaratri, chant along with this devotional song and invoke the blessings of Mata Annapurna Devi for health, prosperity, and happiness.

Celebrate the divine grace of Sri Annapoornadevi with a soulful collection of Annapoornadevi songs and devotional bhajans. During Navaratri, immerse yourself in the spiritual vibrations of Annapoorna Devi Chalisa, Annapoorna stotram, and other powerful Hindu devotional songs dedicated to Maa Annapurna, the goddess of nourishment. These sacred Annapoorna Devi prayers and bhakti songs uplift the soul and bring peace and prosperity. Whether you're seeking the divine through the Sri Annapoorna Chalisa lyrics or enjoying Annapoornadevi Navratri songs, let every note connect you to the eternal mother of abundance.

Lyrics: Mitta Lakshmi
Composer: Solmon Raju
Singer: Mula Srilatha

✨ Sri Annapoornadevi Chalisa is considered highly powerful and is believed to remove scarcity, fulfill wishes, and bless devotees with spiritual growth and peace.

🎶 Listen, Meditate, and Share this soulful Chalisa during Navaratri and immerse yourself in divine devotion.

🌸 Jai Annapoorna Mata 🌸
🌸 Annapurna Devi Ki Jai 🌸
